data.description: Say hello to your new home in the heart of the sweet city of Etowah! Minutes from downtown sits this charming two bedroom and one bath home featuring an updated kitchen, breakfast nook, carport, and fenced in backyard with an outbuilding for extra storage. The living room is complete with a full wall built-in and wait til' you see the big picture window in the dining room. Set up your own private showing today!
